properties.headline: Gale Watch issued January 3 at 3:16AM EST until January 5 at 7:00AM EST by NWS Melbourne FL
properties.description:
* WHAT...Northwest winds 20 to 30 kt with gusts to gale force and
seas building to around 7 feet.

* WHERE...Flagler Beach to Volusia-Brevard County Line 0-20 nm,
Volusia-Brevard County Line to Sebastian Inlet 0-20 nm and
Sebastian Inlet to Jupiter Inlet 0-20 nm.

* WHEN...From Saturday evening through Sunday morning.

* IMPACTS...Strong winds can cause hazardous seas which could
capsize or damage vessels and reduce visibility.
properties.instruction:
Mariners should consider altering plans to avoid possible
hazardous conditions. Remain in port, seek safe harbor, and/or
secure the vessel for possible gale conditions.

NWSheadline: GALE WATCH IN EFFECT FROM SATURDAY EVENING THROUGH SUNDAY MORNING
